title: Exception throws when exporting data from a table containing a highlight and map.
description: Description: An exception is thrown when attempting to export data from the attached report.
OB: When exporting data from a table that contains a group, a highlight rule, and a map rule in the group row, an exception is thrown.
SR: To reproduce the issue: 1. Add a table with a group, a highlight rule, and a map rule in the group row. 2. Preview the attached report.
